Credits to Development Team: Akseli, CrazeNation, and CapitalCoding. I have never had the privilege of working with a team of people who had the combination of hard skills, soft skills, and talents that you all have. We all share the same dream. Making a RSPS that is unique, player driven, and with the sole purpose of reviving the RSPS community. Everyone has been waiting for this server just as long as we have and now it has finally arrived. Lets continue the great work team.
Website - nw-pk.com
-Vinny
